Martin Vaughan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martin_Vaughan 0 Martin Kevin Vaughan (born 5 June 1931) is an Australian stage, television and film actor and musician. He played the lead role in the award-winning 26-part 1976 television series Power Without Glory.
